              <p class="mt-1">In no event shall we be liable to you for any acts or omissions of any Supplier. The limitation of liability set forth in Section B1.2 shall not apply to liability resulting from our gross negligence or willful misconduct. THE FOREGOING DOES NOT AFFECT ANY LIABILITY THAT CANNOT BE EXCLUDED OR LIMITED UNDER APPLICABLE LAW.</p>

              <p class="font-semibold mt-3">B3. Warranty Disclaimers.</p>
              <p>The GetYourGuide Platform, its content, and any services obtained through the GetYourGuide Platform are provided on an "as is" basis, and are available to you without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.</p>

